  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the kabanos sausages and cook until they are browned on all sides.",
    "Add the malted barley flour and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Gradually add the water, stirring constantly to avoid lumps.",
